    /**
     * @description Allows any signed-in user to read local_sales documents.
     * Allows admin, manager, or employee to create, update, or delete local_sales documents.
     * @path /local_sales/{localSaleId}
     * @allow (get, list) Any signed-in user
     * @allow (create, update, delete) Admin, Manager, or Employee role
     * @deny (create, update, delete) Other users
